= PUPPET MODULE:
  jmeter

== REQUIREMENTS:

=== Platform and Application Environment:

Tested on Ubuntu 12.04. May work on other platforms, esp Ubuntu/Debian.

== USAGE:

# Simple default install

class { 'jmeter' : }
include jmeter

# Use external data for packages

class { 'jmeter' : packages => hiera('some_other_packages') }

# Ensure it is not installed

class { 'jmeter' : installed => false }

== CAVEATS:

None.

